Event Name: It ain't gonna puff itself party
Description: If you need a description for this event, it’s not for you.  Come by and enjoy some lively 80’s music, a fancy-ass cocktail, and the biggest “safety meeting” on the hill.  Bonus points for attending naked!

Chocolate Syrup Mud Wrestling – Come by and enjoy some dirty fun.  Get covered in chocolate syrup and have fun taking down your opponent.  We are just down from the showers so cleanup isn’t an issue, or you can just lick each other clean.

Fire Massage – Don’t see the burn, come feel it!  Experience the roar of the fire and the thrill of flames dancing on your skin … feeling the heat; feeling your flesh burn … all without leaving a mark on you.   Our experts will guide you on a journey sure to leave you drooling for more. This is a truly titillating experience for the less hairy folks.  Please do not wear colognes, body lotions, bug spray, or other flammable substances.  We only have one fire extinguisher and she will probably be drunk!

Flogging/Canes – Enjoy the sensations of several types of floggers and canes. We will demonstrate how material, construction, and technique can vary the sensations. This may just inspire you into embrace a side of yourself that you have not discovered.

Sensual play – Imagine you are blindfolded and can’t see.  All you can do is feel …. feel the sensation of fur as it glides delicately along your skin.  Experience a silk scarf exciting your senses. Enjoy the scent and sensation of leather as it caresses you.  A true feast for the senses.  Just say Ahhhhhh.  Safeword not needed.

Massage – Come by and feel the big strong hands removing the stress from your body.  Our self appointed un- LMT, can take you into a whole new dimension of enjoyment.

Knife Play –Knives aren’t just for the kitchen.  Come and enjoy the unique sensation as the cool steel moves over your skin.  Scary?  Yes!  But seductive too. If you’ve even wondered what it would be like making love with Edward Scissorhands, this might be the kink for you.   Even though you may feel you have been sliced open, our experts can guide you on this journey with no cutting or blood involved.  There may be a scratch or two (if you are into that), but chicks/dicks dig scars!

Spanking – Come by and spank or get spanked!  This really needs no explanation.

Free Hugs – Stop by for a free hug from Shameless or give us one.  Hugs make the world a better place.

Who do Voodoo?

Need to exact your revenge on a unsuspecting victim? Are you a guy tired of being told you can't play with dolls? Are you a high ranking member of the Vodouns who wants to lend your skills to this activity? Or maybe just somebody looking for something fun, interesting, and slightly maniacal to do with other like-minded individuals? If you answered yes to any of these questions (or no for that matter), come down to Ragin' Cajun's Who Do da Voodoo doll making party, when you can construct your own talisman of karmic retribution. All supplies included except for one which you will have to aquire yourself (WITH CONSENT!!!). Best of all you keep your doll for life!

*Disclaimer, I am not now and have never claimed to be an actual Voodoo master. No malice intended. Actual results may vary.

Are you a word porn addict like me?! Then I have a surprise for you! I will be hosting a poetry slam for the second year in a row at Alchemy. Come out and get all your feels out before the night truly gets started and we all break away for a wonderful night of poor decisions and unadulterated fun! There will be tears, laughter, rage, and all the other feels you can think of. As well as goodies for people who show up and and feel like reading. Come out and read us some of your work, whether it be poetry, a comedy skit, a letter you wrote to someone that you want to be heard, or even your favorite poem/quote from an wordsmith. There will be a raffle with a special surprise for one winner, so come out and enjoy some word porn with the rest of us addicts!
